s for BLVDM:\n* Campaign automation pipelines\n* Content engines\n* Client dashboards\n* Reporting frameworks\n\n4. Standardize and Scale\n\n* Convert workflows into repeatable templates\n* Ensure systems can be deployed across multiple clients\n* Continuously optimize for efficiency and performance\n\n5. Collaborate with Strategy & Marketing Teams\n\n* Work closely with leadership to align systems with growth objectives\n* Support implementation across client accounts\n\nRequirementsCore Skills\n\n* Experience building AI workflows using LLM APIs (OpenAI, Claude, etc.)\n* Strong understanding of automation tools (Make, Zapier, n8n)\n* Experience integrating systems (CRM, email, WhatsApp, analytics tools)\n* Ability to think in systems, workflows, and scalability\n\nPreferred Background\n\n* Experience in marketing, growth, or business automation systems\n* Understanding of funnels, lead generation, and conversion flows\n* Experience building dashboards and reporting systems\n\nMindset\n\n* Systems thinker (not task executor)\n* Strong problem-solving ability\n* Focused on outcomes, not just tools\n* Ability to work independently and build from scratch\n\nWhat This Role Is Not\n\n* Not a pure machine learning role\n* Not academic AI researcher role\n\nWhat Success Looks Like (First 60 Days)\n\n* Built initial AI content generation system\n* Implemented lead capture and nurture automation\n* Created reporting dashboards for internal/client use\n* Delivered at least 1–2 deployable systems for clients\n\nCompensation\n\n* Competitive (based on experience)\n* Performance-based growth opportunities\n\nHow to Apply\n\nPlease send your application to: clientcare@belvedere-marketing.com\n\nInclude:\n\n* Your resume\n* A brief overview of AI/automation systems you have built\n* A short Loom video (3–5 minutes) explaining:\n* One system you built\n* The problem it solved\n* How it was structured\n\nApplications without the Loom video will not be considered.\n\nFinal Note\n\nWe are building a long-term system-driven company. If you are someone who understands how to turn business problems into scalable AI systems, and wants to be part of building something meaningful, this role is for you.\n\nJob Type: Full-time\n\nWork Location: Remote"}
