{"source":"indeed","source_id":"https://www.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=9a7399f7c3fbc4f6","title":"Associate Director Project Management (Residential)","company":"AtkinsRéalis","location":"{\"city\":\"Abu Dhabi\",\"postalCode\":null,\"country\":\"UAE\",\"countryCode\":\"AE\",\"formattedAddressLong\":\"Abu Dhabi\",\"formattedAddressShort\":\"Abu Dhabi\",\"latitude\":24.46,\"longitude\":54.36,\"streetAddress\":null,\"fullAddress\":null}","remote":false,"salary":"{}","posted_at":"3 months ago","url":"https://www.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=9a7399f7c3fbc4f6","description":"Overview\n\nAs Associate Director, you will be responsible for leading and managing the project or projects within the Masterplan program through the project lifecycle. Work closely with our clients, design consultants, Construction supervision consultant, contractors and other stakeholders to ensure the projects objectives are met in line with our client requirements and expectations.\n\nWith a Strong background in construction management to manage and assist Construction supervision and Contractors meet project and client objectives.\n\nKnowledge of Modern Methods of Construction (MCC) with pre-cast fabrication being consider for the Villa is preferrable.\n\nWill be client facing and assist the Client Senior Manager Delivery ensuring the delivery of the Project though the project life cycle.\n\nYou will assist the Programme Director and support Senior Project Manager in ensuring that our scope of works is delivered to AtkinsRéalis and client's'expectations.\n\nYour role\n\nProgramme Delivery & Integration\n\nSupport the Project Director in ensuring consistent PMC delivery across villa and infrastructure packages.\nLead risk management, escalation, and resolution of issues impacting multiple packages or disciplines.\nMonitor interface between design, construction, and commercial teams to ensure delivery cohesion.\nEnsure compliance with delegated responsibilities under FIDIC where PMC is the named Engineer (site