esign delivery.\nEnsure AtkinsRéalis processes, forms and deliverables are followed, and when required, client processes and forms as applicable in full consultation with the client.\nManage, direct, lead and administrate the contracts of the various entities on the Program:\nLead Design Consultant (LDC)\nOther consultants appointed by the client.\nConstruction Supervision Consultant (CSC)\nEarly Works and Main Work Contractors\nShall coordinate and assist activities and work with various entities on the program:\nStakeholders not limited to: Client teams, tenants, facility management, operators etc.\nConsultants and Contractors\nStatutory Authorities with support of Stakeholder Manager\nConstruction Supervision Consultant (CSC)\nLogistics with support of logistics officer and assisted by client.\nManage and assist the client with the procurement of Design Consultant, specialists and Contractors as and when required.\nOverall awareness of PMC scope of services to manage and assist with, but not limited to:\nConstruction Management\nConstructability\nSafety in Design\nAssist in Change Management of the Project with the Cost and Commercial Teams, implement required change control processes, review and recommendation for Client confirmation.\nAssist and coordinate value management during the Design and construction stages in support of the Client.\nDetermine and manage risks that may affect the programme/project not limited to schedule, budget, client requirements, quality, constructability and compliance.\nAssist on monitoring and managing the Design and construction schedule with Project Controls and LDC\nAssist in Stakeholder Management: Develop the statutory approval workflow chart for all design stages and in alignment with Client and Statutory Authority approval requirements.\nOversee preparation of all technical documentation required for construction tender packages.\nPerform other duties as assigned.\nAbout you\n\nQualifications\n\nBachelor's degree in architecture, Civil Engineering, or relevant design discipline; Chartered status (e.g., RIBA, P. Eng, C. Eng) preferred.\nAble to work in a team environment and be client facing.\nActive leadership style.\n\nExperience\n\n20-25 years working experience with experience in the region preferrable.\nWith 10+ years' experience in UAE in design manager experience on hospitality projects.\nPreferable 5+ years in Project Management Consultancy.\nPost-Contract experience mainly with both Pre - Post Contract preferrable.\n\nCompetencies\n\nDeep knowledge of FIDIC contract implementation (including delegated site roles).\nExcellent stakeholder engagement and risk management capabilities.\nProven authority coordination and PMC delivery experience.\nStrong cross-functional leadership and commercial awareness.\nRewards & benefits\n\nExplore the rewards and benefits that help you thrive – at every stage of your life and your career.\n\nThis includes:\n\nTax-free salary.\nComprehensive life insurance coverage.\nPremium medical insurance for you and your dependents.\nGenerous annual leave balance.\nFlexible and hybrid work solutions.\nRemote work opportunities outside of country.\nCompany gratuity scheme.\nDiscretionary bonus program.\nAnnual flight contribution.\nRelocation assistance.\nTransportation & housing allowances (available for remote work locations).\nEmployee Wellbeing Program: 24/7 access to specialists in finance, legal matters, family care, personal health, fitness, and nutrition.\n\nSeize every opportunity to sharpen your skills, expand your expertise, and be recognized for the impact you make.\n\nAbout AtkinsRéalis\n\nWe're AtkinsRéalis, a world-class engineering services and nuclear organization. We connect people, data and technology to transform the world's'infrastructure and energy systems. Together, with our industry partners and clients, and our global team of consultants, designers, engineers and project managers, we can change the world. We're committed to leading our clients across our various end markets to engineer a better future for our planet and its people.\n\n#HC #ProjectLeadership #AtkinsRealis"}
