cy.\n\n*6. Financial & Cost Control*\n\n* Monitor operational budgets and delivery costs.\n* Improve profitability through route optimization and workforce efficiency.\n* Support finance in invoicing and cost analysis.\n\n*7. Compliance & Risk Management*\n\n* Ensure compliance with UAE laws, safety standards, and company policies.\n* Identify operational risks and implement mitigation plans.\n\n*8. Process Improvement & Systems*\n\n* Improve operational workflows and automate processes.\n* Ensure proper use of ERP systems and delivery platforms.\n* Use data analytics to enhance decision-making.\n\n*9. Leadership & Reporting*\n\n* Lead and develop operations teams.\n* Provide reports and insights to senior management.\n* Drive a culture of accountability and performance excellence.\n\n*Qualifications & Requirements*\n\n* Bachelor’s degree in Business Administration, Logistics, or related field.\n* 5–8+ years of experience in delivery, logistics, or operations management.\n* Strong experience in last-mile delivery operations (preferred in UAE/GCC).\n* Knowledge of delivery platforms and fleet operations.\n\n*Key Skills*\n\n* Leadership & team management\n* Logistics & supply chain management\n* Data analysis & KPI tracking\n* Problem-solving & decision-making\n* Communication & stakeholder management\n* Route optimization & planning\n\n*Work Environment (*United Arab Emirates *and Gulf )*\n\n* Fast-paced operations environment.\n* Requires field visits and coordination with drivers/fleet.\n* Interaction with government regulations and transport compliance in the United Arab Emirates and Gulf.\n\nJob Type: Full-time\n\nPay: From AED5,000.00 per month\n\nWork Location: Remote"}
